<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8"
	pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<style>
.pitnik-title {
	margin-top: 40x;
	margin-bottom: 40px;
	text-align: center;
}

.page-createbox .row>div {
	margin-bottom: 20px;
	padding: 0 70px;
}

</style>

<div class="col-lg-12">
	<div class="pitnik-title">
		<h1>🙋 1:1 문의하기 작성</h1>
		<p>※ 상담사에게 폭언, 욕설 등을 하지 말아 주세요. 답변을 받지 못하거나 사전안내 없이 삭제될 수 있습니다.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="central-meta">
		<span class="create-post">문의하기</span>
		<div class="page-createbox">
			<form method="post" class="c-form">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-lg-12">
						<div class="title1">문의유형</div>
						<select class="form-control" style="width: 100%;">
							<option>상품</option>
							<option>결제</option>
							<option>배송</option>
							<option>기타문의사항</option>
						</select>
					</div>
					<div class="col-lg-12">
						<div class="title1">제목</div>
						<div class="social-name">
							<input type="text" placeholder="문의 제목을 입력해주세요 ! ">
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="col-lg-12">
						<div class="title1">문의내용</div>
						<textarea rows="5px" placeholder="문의하실 내용을 입력해주세요 !"></textarea>
					</div>
					<div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-top:30px;">
						<button class="main-btn" type="submit" data-ripple="">등록</button>
						<button class="main-btn3" type="submit" data-ripple="">취소</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>